<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263417>
    dc:description "PLATE 116. Leptadrillia splendida, Bartsch, 1934. Figs. 1 – 3: holotype, Samaná Bay, Dominican Republic (USNM 429368). Fig. 1: ventral, lateral & dorsal views; Fig. 2: enlarged view of protoconch (not to scale); Fig. 3: apical view, V = varix, L = edge of outer lip. Figs. 4 – 6: Altona Bay, St. Croix, U. S. Virgin Is., ventral views (AMNH 192601)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263417/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

